<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TCV80">
<l>vāciyāki nēcamiṉṟi vantetirnta tēṉukaṉ</l>
<l>nācamāki nāḷulappa naṉmaicērpa ṉaṅkaṉikku</l>
<l>vīcamēṉi mirntatōḷi lillaiyākki ṉāykaḻaṟ</l>
<l>kācaiyāma varkkalāla mararāka lākumē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>You threw Dhenuka—who came without love as a donkey and attacked [You]—</l>
<l>From [Your] uplifted shoulders, onto the good woodapple fruits</l>
<l rend="indent">so that [he] is destroyed, with [his] days getting spent up.</l>
<l>Who other than the people who desire the feet of</l>
<l>You, who [thus] annihilated [Dhenuka], can become immortal?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
